# combined — __ipow__, __ilshift__, __irshift__ across representative io subjects
#
# 8 classes x 3 methods = 24 rows.
# All three in-place power/shift dunder methods are absent from all
# io class __dict__s: all false. io stream classes are I/O abstractions, not
# numeric or bitwise types, and have no augmented-assignment semantics for
# exponentiation or bit-shift.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

